214
00:12:02,067 --> 00:12:03,167
Aqui.

215
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:04,333
Eh?

216
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:07,200
Feliz aniversário!

217
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,600
